    <td>Backpack upgrade item</td>
    <td>Upgrade item used to further improve the backpack</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<div class="tip"><strong>Mercury source:</strong> Mercury ore found in Swamp biome (Y 0–40). Requires @3 furnace (Obsidian Furnace) to smelt!</div>

